  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Voulez Vous is offered on a half board basis. </p>
<p>Meals are served in <em>Il Savoia</em> restaurant.  Each day fuel up for the day at the breakfast buffet which has a range of bread, cheese and charcuterie sourced from local suppliers, seasonal fruits, local delicacies and an assortment of sweet and savoury treats. </p>
<p>Dinner is a fusion of Italian and French Savoie traditions, two of the worlds greatest gastronomies. You could enjoy dishes such as Truffle pizza, roasted meats and risottos.</p>
<p>As part of the half-board option, you can also enjoy dinner in a few of the nearby Etincelles resturants including Le Chalet, La Brasserie De L'Arbina, Aiguille Percee and Les Terrasses Du Levanna. Please enquire with the reception regarding availability.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
