  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Comfort Rooms</strong> are around 18m² sleeping two people in a king size bed, and have panoramic views of the village and mountains. </p>
<p><strong>Cosy Rooms</strong> are more spacious at around 25m² sleeping two people in a king size bed, and have panoramic views of the village and mountains. Some rooms may have a balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Privilege Rooms</strong> are around 30m² sleeping up to three people. The rooms have a king size bed and a armchair made up as an additional bed (suitable for children up to 12 years old). <span> </span></p>
<p><strong>Privilege Rooms with Balcony </strong>are around 30m² sleeping up to three people. Each of these rooms have a king size bed and an armchair made up as an additional bed (suitable for children up to 12 years old) and a balcony with mountain or village views. </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Beds can be made up as twin beds on request</li>
<li>Tea and coffee facilities</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Welcome amenities</li>
<li>Bathrobe and slippers</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>All rooms have an ensuite with shower </li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
